$('#test').nth();

It will add classes to the child elements like...

<ol id="test" class="indexed">
    <li class="nth-1 nth-2n-plus-1 nth-2n-minus-1 nth-3n-plus-1 nth-3n-minus-2 nth-4n-plus-1 nth-4n-minus-3">item 1</li>
    <li class="nth-2 nth-2n nth-3n-plus-2 nth-3n-minus-1 nth-4n-plus-2 nth-4n-minus-2">item 2</li>
    <li class="nth-3 nth-2n-plus-1 nth-2n-minus-1 nth-3n nth-4n-plus-3 nth-4n-minus-1">item 3</li>
    <li class="nth-4 nth-2n nth-3n-plus-1 nth-3n-minus-2 nth-4n">item 4</li>
</ol>